title: Getting Started with API Testing
body: API testing is an essential skill for modern software development. This tutorial covers the basics of API testing using JavaScript.

title: Advanced Testing Patterns
body: Learn about advanced testing patterns including Page Object Model, Data Builder, and Fluent Interface patterns.

title: Performance Testing Guide
body: Comprehensive guide to performance testing including load testing, stress testing, and performance optimization techniques.

title: Security Testing Best Practices
body: Learn about security testing including OWASP Top 10, SQL injection, XSS, and other common vulnerabilities.

title: CI/CD Integration
body: How to integrate API testing into your CI/CD pipeline using Jenkins, GitHub Actions, and other tools.
